mods.abstract: The pyramidalized olefin 1 is the key intermediate for the synthesis of bridgehead-substituted tribenzotriquinacenes. Intermediate 1 allows access to up to fourfold substituted tribenzoquinacenes as readily as to the unsubstituted cyclopropatribenzoquinacene.
